Time & life
life flows through time
time blends with life 
theyre not what they are
without each other

life creates purpose
purpose is limited with time
time created memories
memories are shared throughout life

life is growing constantly
it takes years and years to develope
we live longer & longer
but it seems shorter & shorter

A heartbeat is a patturn of time
each heartbeatyou hear represents
a moment in your life
no matter how small it seems

life & time both take course
in what we call a process
and the process in this world happens
only once in a human and never stops

Katie keen Dec 7th 2006
